249
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:45,507
Sekarang tentu lebih mudah.

250
00:26:48,385 --> 00:26:49,427
Ada apa?

251
00:26:50,136 --> 00:26:51,304
Gwang-cheol.

252
00:26:52,138 --> 00:26:53,014
Kau berpikir sama?

253
00:26:55,642 --> 00:26:57,560
Apa? Ada apa sebenarnya?

254
00:26:58,812 --> 00:26:59,896
Kau bilang lebih mudah.

255
00:27:00,730 --> 00:27:02,232
