256
00:27:03,274 --> 00:27:04,484
Ini lebih mudah.

257
00:27:04,567 --> 00:27:07,320
Lebih mudah karena mereka
hanya di sel penahanan.

258
00:27:07,946 --> 00:27:09,447
Coba pikirkan caranya.

259
00:27:11,825 --> 00:27:13,868
Apa maksudmu?

260
00:27:13,952 --> 00:27:15,120
Kenapa kau begini?

261
00:27:15,829 --> 00:27:17,914
Kalian berdua sudah gila?

262
