266
00:27:37,183 --> 00:27:38,810
Buat apa bertengkar dengan polisi?

267
00:27:39,352 --> 00:27:41,104
Sepertinya ada musuh lain bagiku.

268
00:27:41,729 --> 00:27:43,064
