302
00:30:59,135 --> 00:31:00,219
Selamat tinggal.

303
00:31:01,888 --> 00:31:03,389
Kang Gi-beom.

304
00:31:04,724 --> 00:31:06,476
Dalang dari semua ini.

305
00:31:06,726 --> 00:31:09,562
